},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"cb65f5",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Methylxanthines (theophylline, aminophylline; sustained and short-acting)"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"3f4524",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Tachycardia, nausea, vomiting, and disturbed sleep; narrow therapeutic index; overdose can be fatal with seizures and arrhythmias"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"18db6a",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Used as maintenance therapy; generally used only after long-acting bronchodilator treatment to provide additional symptomatic relief of exacerbations; may also improve respiratory muscle function"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
